perf: Optimize backend efficiency and caching

- Add lightweight in-memory cache utility with TTL support
- Cache Gemini API responses to eliminate redundant network calls
- Optimize polling distance algorithm by removing redundant Math.sqrt calls
- Cache polling search and nearest booth queries
- Replace Array.sort shuffle with O(n) Fisher-Yates algorithm in quiz service
- Add unit tests for cache utility (186 total tests, all passing)
- Maintain clean architecture and strict security standards
